{"id":3071,"date":"2025-05-17T10:59:29","date_gmt":"2025-05-17T03:59:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=3071"},"modified":"2025-12-05T15:03:44","modified_gmt":"2025-12-05T08:03:44","slug":"dien-di-anh-sang-voi-mun-trung-ca","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/dien-di-anh-sang-voi-mun-trung-ca\/","title":{"rendered":"\u0110i\u1ec7n di &#038; \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u00e0nh cho da m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1, m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam trung b\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1eb7ng.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 gom c\u1ed3i m\u1ee5n, gi\u1ea3m s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/li>\n<li>Ki\u1ec1m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u nh\u1eddn, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba m\u1ee5n m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh th\u00e0nh.<\/li>\n<li>An to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Chemical Peel &#8211; S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c acid h\u1eefu c\u01a1 n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p (AHA, BHA&#8230;) th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y thay m\u1edbi t\u1ebf b\u00e0o.<\/li>\n<li>K\u00edch th\u00edch c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o da bong tr\u00f3c, t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o l\u00e0n da m\u1edbi gi\u1ea3m m\u1ee5n se c\u1ed3i m\u1ee5n, gi\u1ea3m vi\u00eam, gi\u1ea3m ti\u1ebft d\u1ea7u, s\u00e1ng da, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p t\u1ebf b\u00e0o g\u1ed1c m\u1ee5n v\u1edbi Sulfur 2.28%, Retinol 0.05%, Bakuchiol.<\/li>\n<li>Gi\u1ea3m t\u00e1i vi\u00eam sau li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh, gi\u1ea3m s\u01b0ng n\u1ec1n, l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da sau n\u1eb7n m\u1ee5n v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da m\u1ee5n t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 60 ph\u00fat<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng 05 bu\u1ed5i, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i c\u00e1ch nhau 21 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -1px; top: 392.563px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u00e0nh cho da m\u1ee5n tr\u1ee9ng c\u00e1, m\u1ee5n vi\u00eam trung b\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1eb7ng.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3626,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[59],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-3071","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-advanced-skincare-therapy","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/3071","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/product"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3071"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3626"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3071"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"product_brand","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_brand?post=3071"},{"taxonomy":"product_cat","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_cat?post=3071"},{"taxonomy":"product_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product_tag?post=3071"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}